| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3409 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5a917cbe-1bfc-5d52-8fe7-7e48a3d2b336"
